Doug,
This email serves as formal notice regarding client credentials, client-sys=
tem access, and communication protocol.
Technijian has been informed that you recently sought client credentials an=
d access information by contacting Technijian personnel other than me, incl=
uding requests for Brandywine/BWH server and ESXi credentials and for the A=
OC firewall password. You are not authorized to request, receive, or obtain=
 client credentials, passwords, or access information directly from Technij=
ian employees.
Effective immediately, all communications, requests, and inquiries relating=
 in any way to Technijian, its personnel, its clients, client environments,=
 client systems, client credentials, or access to client resources must be =
directed solely to me, in writing, by email. You are not authorized to cont=
act Technijian administrative staff, technical staff, or any other Techniji=
an personnel directly concerning those matters.
Technijian has legal, contractual, security, and confidentiality obligation=
s with respect to client information, client systems, and access credential=
s. Accordingly, Technijian must control, review, and document any request r=
elating to client access or client credentials. No client credentials, pass=
words, or access information will be provided except through a process expr=
essly authorized and administered by Technijian.
You are directed not to make any further direct requests to Technijian pers=
onnel for passwords, firewall credentials, server credentials, ESXi credent=
ials, administrative access, or any other client-related access information=
. If you believe there is a legitimate business basis for any requested acc=
ess, you must submit that request to me by email, and Technijian will revie=
w and respond in writing as it determines appropriate.
For the avoidance of doubt, this notice is intended to protect client relat=
ionships, preserve Technijian=92s contractual and security obligations, and=
 ensure that all communications and access-related requests are handled in =
a controlled and documented manner. This direction is effective immediately=
 and is to be followed strictly going forward.
Thank you,

[Ravi Jain]
